ea5t ch\u1ea5p l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1eafng 4-1 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\">Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 AS Roma l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</span> khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd v\u00e0 c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u ra \u0111i v\u00ec lu\u1eadt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">\u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid c\u0169ng su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi \u0111\u00e1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1</span>, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn 3-0 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA vs Arsenal Wenger lay Barca canh bao hoc tro hinh anh\" title=\"CSKA vs Arsenal Wenger l\u1ea5y Barca c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/wenger-lay-barca-lam-bai-hoc-canh-tinh-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng nh\u01b0 Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn CSKA vs Arsenal t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Europa League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn CSKA vs Arsenal t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Europa League 2017/18, Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi l\u1ea5y Barca ra l\u00e0m b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1u, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-1 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Wenger:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i xem tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh n\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng ng\u00f3 qua b\u00ean kia. Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Roma \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf n\u00ean, <em><strong>\u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c cho t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan, s\u01a1 h\u1edf</strong></em>, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 Europa League. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i hay c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn CSKA vs Arsenal:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-2h05-ngay-134-lieu-co-dia-chan-184-184081.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-2h05-ngay-134-lieu-co-dia-chan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-2h05-ngay-134-lieu-co-dia-chan-184-184081.html\">CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal (2h05 ng\u00e0y 13/4): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng mong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, b\u1edfi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1080","checkdouble":"184086"},{"date":"10:46 12/04","title":"\"Th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i\" Vazquez n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/vazquez-noi-gi-ve-qua-penalty-gay-tranh-cai-o-tran-gap-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;heigh