.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t penalty cho Real, \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\u2019 Lucas Vazquez \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League 2017/18 </span>gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Juventus, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Lucas Vazquez \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi Juve.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez noi ve qua penalty o tran gap Juventus - Bong da 24 hinh anh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Juventus - B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/vazquez-noi-gi-ve-qua-penalty-gay-tranh-cai-o-tran-gap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Vazquez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c trong t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i penalty cho Real l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Medhi Benatia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Vazquez tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng Michael Oliver \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Real nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1eeb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sai v\u00e0 \u01b0u \u00e1i Real.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, trong th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\u2019 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-muon-real-ban-lucas-vazquez-180-174177.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Vazquez</span> \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 11m\u201d, Vazquez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u201cBenatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1n ng\u00e3 khi t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 60 ph\u00fat. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HVL Zidane c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Real-Madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid</span> \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd qua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u00f9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. D\u00f9 trong b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u00f3i th\u00eam.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chu-tich-juve-muon-uefa-thay-doi-luat-sau-tran-thua-real-madrid-184-184078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/chu-tich-juve-muon-uefa-thay-doi-luat-sau-tran-thua-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chu-tich-juve-muon-uefa-thay-doi-luat-sau-tran-thua-real-madrid-184-184078.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juve mu\u1ed1n UEFA thay \u0111\u1ed5i lu\u1eadt sau tr\u1eadn thua Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Juventus, \u00f4ng Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u UEFA s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1079","checkdouble":"184087"},{"date":"10:58 12/04","title":"Barca b\u1ecb Roma \u201c\u0111\u00e1 bay\u201d kh\u1ecfi Champions League: Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/barca-bi-roma-loai-khoi-champions-league-khong-dep-khong-co-quyen.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f