u00e3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Kane tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi hay ch\u01b0a. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho Christian Eriksen v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Spurs kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh \u0111ang <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/kane-tuyen-chien-salah-trong-cuoc-dua-vua-pha-luoi-172-183860.html\">\u0111ua tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League 2017/18</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane bi Salah mia mai vi duoc uu ai Vua pha luoi Premier League hinh anh\" title=\"Kane b\u1ecb Salah m\u1ec9a mai v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/doi-lai-cong-bang-harry-kane-bi-doi-thu-salah-mia-mai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea1nh tranh Mo Salah trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Harry Kane c\u00f2n th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn chia s\u1ebb suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t g\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau \u0111\u00f3: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ec1 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng s\u1ed1ng con g\u00e1i m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khai cho ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tottenham l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi <em><strong>b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1edd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn cho Harry Kane</strong></em>, gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 25 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League 2017/18.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mo-salah-messi-ai-cap-hay-mot-su-so-sanh-lo-bich-172-183227.html\">\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh Mo Salah</span> c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i 180 \u0111\u1ed9 \u01b0u \u00e1i Harry Kane c\u1ee7a ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u1ec9a mai \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u201cG\u00ec c\u01a1, th\u1eadt sao?\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Salah v\u1eabn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League 2017/18 v\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Harry Kane. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong khi Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 5 tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u, Tottenham v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">\u00a0\u00a0 </span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane vs Mo Salah \u2013 Ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League 2017/18?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-tottenham-muon-harry-kane-nhu-totti-hay-doi-xu-anh-nhu-totti-172-181239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/3/goc-tottenham-muon-harry-kane-nhu-totti-hay-doi-xu-anh-nhu-totti.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-tottenham-muon-harry-kane-nhu-totti-hay-doi-xu-anh-nhu-totti-172-181239.html\">G\u00f3c Tottenham: Mu\u1ed1n Kane nh\u01b0 Totti, ch\u0103m Kane nh\u01b0 Totti</span><br>\r\nH\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c, b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb, kh\u00f4ng xa hoa v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n tr\u00e1nh xa nh\u1eefng \u1ed3n \u00e0o, th\u1ecb phi, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n one-club man c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-liverpool-salah-da-thuc-su-la-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi-172-183960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/goc-liverpool-salah-da-thuc-su-la-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-liverpoo