nnel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Christian Eriksen trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Stoke, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3 m\u1ea1ng s\u1ed1ng con g\u00e1i ra th\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan ung hai huoc cua Mohamed Salah khi hay tin Harry Kane doi ban thang thanh cong.\" title=\"Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah khi hay tin Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/30697682_208460269928399_2393730749127446734_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah khi hay tin Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng: &quot;Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y \u00e0?&quot;.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer m\" title=\"Alan Shearer m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alan Shearer m\u1ec9a mai vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: &quot;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd vui l\u1eafm n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd cho m\u00ecnh th\u00eam 9 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa&quot;.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dong doi Georginio Wijnaldum dung anh dong hai huoc de phan ung viec Harry Kane doi ban thang thanh cong.\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Georginio Wijnaldum d\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/30628943_1650748098378524_812310793939845120_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Georginio Wijnaldum d\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Lineker cung mia mai:\" title=\"Gary Lineker c\u0169ng m\u1ec9a mai:\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/30629119_10209185779236091_2519483199768336859_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gary Lineker c\u0169ng m\u1ec9a mai: &quot;B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mandzukic gi\u1edd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh cho Harry Kane&quot;.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n<