play:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Manchester United m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford. Theo \u0111\u00f3, MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTin \u0111\u1ed3n Rashford ch\u00e1n M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi ra m\u1eaft Man United d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Louis van Gaal t\u1edbi nay, Marcus Rashford lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 31 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau 2 m\u00f9a r\u01b0\u1ee1i ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Rashford c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 2 t\u1edbi nay, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-marcus-rashford-khong-nen-roi-mu-172-183946.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Rashford t\u1ea1i M.U</strong></span> l\u1ea1i r\u1ed9 l\u00ean c\u00f3 tin anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u00f3 8 ph\u00fat \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Manchester.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong MU khong ban Rashford voi bat cu gia nao hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/11/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Rashford \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a Rashford<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-marcus-rashford-khong-nen-roi-mu-172-183946.html\" target=\"_blank\"></span> l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp b\u00f9ng l\u00ean. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh loan tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng bao g\u1ed3m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-arsenal-khuyen-bo-doi-sao-tre-som-roi-mu-172-184058.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright cho r\u1eb1ng Rashford n\u00ean r\u1eddi M.U</strong></span> \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u00f4n v\u00f9i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ESPN v\u1eeba \u0111\u0103ng tin M.U quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Marcus Rashford c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Hi\u1ec7n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c. H\u1ecd quan ni\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua Rashford trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford phat bieu ve Mourinho\" title=\"Rashford phat bieu ve Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Bi-dung-cham-vu-Rashford,-Mourinho-chua-ngoa-dap-tra-dong-nghiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 2 n\u0103m, Rashford \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi M.U k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Barcelona v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-mua-rashford-sao-tre-bi-that-sung-cua-mu-180-182693.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Rashford</strong></span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng tin MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trung (20 tu\u1ed5i), l\u1ea1i \u0111a n\u0103ng (ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 trung phong l\u1eabn hai c\u00e1nh) nh\u01b0 Rashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-southampton-172-184042.html\">M.U chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Southampton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league-172-184020.html\">M.U nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-dau-hieu-lon-cho-thay-trung-ve-samuel-umtiti-den-mu-180-183956.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y Umtiti s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-va-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-183921.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u00e0 Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-phu-nhan-chieu-mo-sao-mu-172-183918.html\">Liverpool ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/huyen-thoai-real-giup-mu-dinh-gia-gareth-bale-180-183908.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real gi\u00fap M.U \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1075","checkdouble":"184092"},{"date":"09:13 12/04","title":"Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Buffon tr\u01b0\u1ed