adn Real vs Juventus, HLV Allegri l\u1ea1i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 penalty oan nghi\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u00fac v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng gi\u00fap Real c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Qua \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-champions-league-201718-372-184054.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus</strong></span> sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Bayern Munich, Liverpool v\u00e0 AS Roma l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon phan ung trong tai tran Real vs Juventus duoc thong cam hinh anh\" title=\"Buffon ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Buffon-phan-ung-trong-tai-tran-Real-vs-Juventus-duoc-thong-cam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Michael Oliver v\u00ec x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Medhi Benatia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Lucas Vazquez trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Gianluigi Buffon \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Sau tr\u1eadn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buffon n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver</strong></span> v\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Allegri th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec tr\u00e1ch m\u1eafng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang-184-184073.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Allegri tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n</strong></span> l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng h\u00e0nh vi Buffon ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. &ldquo;C\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai s\u00f3t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo;, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus n\u00f3i. &ldquo;Gigi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan ung cua Buffon truoc Real co the thong cam duoc hinh anh 2\" title=\"Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Buffon tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/buffon-phan-ung-trong-tai-tran-real-vs-juventus-co-the-thong-cam-duoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Buffon ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus </span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Champions League cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Gigi hay kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 vu\u1ed9t kh\u1ecfi tay c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec3u ti\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 