(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng mong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, b\u1edfi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u mong ch\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4-1, Arsenal d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 CSKA Moscow tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Aaron Ramsey v\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League 2017-18. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal va Man Utd deu no luc tai Europa League de gianh quyen du Champions League.\" title=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Europa League \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/tu-arsenal-va-man-utd-europa-league-gio-la-lanh-dia-cua-nguoi-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Arsene Wenger c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAS Roma h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Barca tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Juventus su\u00fdt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n n\u1eefa tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu d\u00f9 thua 0-3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Viktor Goncharenko s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n VEB Arena.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafng CSKA Moscow tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf d\u00f9 hai \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p nhau m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League 2006-07, Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 0-1 khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, phong \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 10 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Arsenal ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock out Europa League g\u1eb7p Ostersunds r\u1ed3i AC Milan, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn 6 tr\u1eadn thua. B\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, phong \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 18 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ngo\u1ea1i giao gi\u1eefa Nga v\u00e0 Anh, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u00f3m Ultras hung h\u00e3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ec7nh d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga, Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 e ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n VEB Arena.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal\" title=\"Preview CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-2h05-ngay-134-lieu-co-dia-chan.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal?</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dynamo Moscow tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn CSKA r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Russian Premier League (gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Nga). H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai Spartak Moscow. Theo th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i, n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League 2018-19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau, CSKA Moscow ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG, ho\u1eb7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee9 hai c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n xa x\u0103m nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u1eb3ng ai n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League. HLV Arsene Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ecfng ch\u00e2n d\u00f9 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, b\u1edfi &quot;ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau 3 l\u1ea7n, v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow v\u00e0 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 0-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Arsenal c\u0169ng th\u1eafng 5 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Europa League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>CSKA Moscow:</strong> Viktor Vasin, Mario Fernandes ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal: </strong>Santi Cazorla, Henrikh Mkhitaryan ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Granit Xhaka, Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n - David Ospina ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal (2h05 ng\u00e0y 11/4):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>CSKA Moscow (3-5-2): </strong>35.Akinfeev - 6.A.Berezutski, 24.VBerezutski, 4.Ignashevich - 89.Kuchaev, 10.Dzagoev, 66.Natkho, 17.Golovin, 14.Nababkin - 7.Musa, 3.Wernbloom</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal (4-2-3-1):</strong> 33.Cech - 24.Bellerin, 20.Mustafi, 6.Koscielny, 18.Monreal - 8.Ramsey,29. Xhaka - 23.Welbeck, 10.Wilshere, 11.Mesut Ozil - 9.Lacazette</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> CSKA Moscow 1-1 Arsenal<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/CSKA-Moscow-vs-Arsenal-(3-5-2-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-arsenal-khuyen-bo-doi-sao-tre-som-roi-mu-172-184058.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal khuy\u00ean b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb s\u1edbm r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-psg-tranh-gianh-kenedy-172-184027.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/doanh-thu-cua-arsenal-hua-hen-tang-manh-neu-bo-puma-theo-adidas-188-183935.html\">Doanh thu c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf Puma theo Adidas</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mkhitaryan-bat-ngo-da-xoay-mourinho-va-man-utd-172-183898.html\">Mkhitaryan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y Mourinho v\u00e0 Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nhan-tin-soc-tu-chan-thuong-cua-mkhitaryan-172-183888.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin s\u1ed1c t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/watford-chot-gia-ban-hang-hot-richarlison-172-183879.html\">Watford ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng hot Richarlison</span></div>\r\n</div>\r