\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Juventus, \u00f4ng Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u UEFA s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video) \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Juventus tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu t\u1ed1i qua, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juve d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1edbi 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Real v\u1eabn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi thua chung cu\u1ed9c 3-4 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.\u00a0\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Seria A \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong su\u1ed1t 90 v\u00e0 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n trong hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng l\u01a1 l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng khi Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 penalty, sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Lucas Vazquez b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 Medhi Benatia x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 trong khu c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chu tich Juventus muon UEFA thay doi luat sau tran thua Real hinh anh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juventus mu\u1ed1n UEFA thay \u0111\u1ed5i lu\u1eadt sau tr\u1eadn thua Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/chu-tich-juve-muon-uefa-thay-doi-luat-sau-tran-thua-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juventus hy v\u1ecdng UEFA s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR t\u1ea1i Champions League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Lucas Vazquez b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i 11m, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Juventus, \u00f4ng Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u UEFA s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video) \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eca n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi ph\u00e1n quy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Cuadrado, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Milan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal, v\u00e0 Juve t\u1ed1i nay. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang ta r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR t\u1ea1i Champions League\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cao \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juventus c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Juve v\u1eeba di\u1ec5n ra.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Andrea Agnelli n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay th\u1eadt t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juve \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u00e3y mang v\u00e0o \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Champions League. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd sau khi xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1072","checkdouble":"184078"},{"date":"08:12 12/04","title":"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus b\u1ee9c x\u00fac t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/chiellini-to-trong-tai-thien-vi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.artic