ing: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Juventus, Giorgio Chiellini \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Real mua chu\u1ed9c.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League 2017/18</span> di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Bernabeu r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay 12/4 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 L\u00e3o b\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00ec thua 3-4 chung cu\u1ed9c sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac cau thu Juventus buc xuc to trong tai thien vi Real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus b\u1ee9c x\u00fac t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/chiellini-to-trong-tai-thien-vi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chiellini t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 Giorgio Chiellini \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Real x\u1eed \u00e9p. Chiellini b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: &quot;Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ea3. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bayern Munich t\u1eebng thua theo k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y (thua Real \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft - PV) v\u00e0 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Juve. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb x\u1eed \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn Juve d\u00ednh penalty l\u00e0 Mehdi Benatia l\u1ea1i thanh minh: &quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng. Vazquez ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng v\u00ec anh ta ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y ra t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 l\u00fd.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i theo \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i Bayern c\u0169ng \u1edf t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao Real l\u1ea1i hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i penalty d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 va ch\u1ea1m nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Juve l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro c\u0169ng ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m vi\u1ec7c Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i. &quot;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1c v\u00e0 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi b\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i Real, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Juventus xin thua lu\u00f4n. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i&quot;, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil cho hay.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus</strong><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088661/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real vs Juve</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"https://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\">\u00d4ng ta l\u00e0 k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e1u l\u1ea1nh, k\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"https://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-va-ky-niem-buon-trong-tran-cuoi-cung-tai-champions-league-184-184069.html\">Buffon v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"https://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-juventus-xung-dang-nhan-duoc-nhung-loi-khen-ngoi-184-184066.html\">Buffon: Juventus x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"https://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\">Zidane: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div c