y>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jupp Heynckes phat bieu ve tran Bayern Munich vs Sevilla hinh anh\" title=\"Jupp Heynckes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Jupp-Heynckes-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Bayern-Munich-vs-Sevilla-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sven Ulreich \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nh\u00e0n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Bayern d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 18 l\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch 6 song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David Soria \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Anh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-bayern-munich-vs-sevilla-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-184055.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Bayern Munich vs Sevilla </strong></span>\u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Heynckes h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jupp Heynckes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jupp Heynckes phat bieu ve tran Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" title=\"Jupp Heynckes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jupp Heynckes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cSevilla l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eafng 2-1, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Bayern, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ghi b\u00e0n. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Bayern \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJupp Heynckes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n: \u201c3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1067","checkdouble":"184067"},{"date":"06:27 12/04","title":"Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Montella ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/thay-tro-montella-nghen-ngao-noi-loi-chia-tay-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#